<item>
<title>碎片化阅读：行尸走肉的精神食粮</title>
<link>http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/jlwl1zq55R</link>
<guid isPermaLink="true" >http://www.jintiankansha.me/t/jlwl1zq55R</guid>
<description>&lt;p rgb=&quot;rgb&quot; important=&quot;important&quot; border-box=&quot;border-box&quot; em=&quot;em&quot; break-word=&quot;break-word&quot; normal=&quot;normal&quot; px=&quot;px&quot; sans-serif=&quot;sans-serif&quot; arial=&quot;arial&quot; yahei=&quot;yahei&quot; microsoft=&quot;microsoft&quot; ui=&quot;ui&quot; gb=&quot;gb&quot; sans=&quot;sans&quot; hiragino=&quot;hiragino&quot; sc=&quot;sc&quot; pingfang=&quot;pingfang&quot; neue=&quot;neue&quot; helvetica=&quot;helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;阅读是补充自身输入的一个好方法，经常有小伙伴问我为什么了解那么多，无非就是多读多看多输入，再经过自己思考加工，才能够有输出。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p rgb=&quot;rgb&quot; important=&quot;important&quot; border-box=&quot;border-box&quot; em=&quot;em&quot; break-word=&quot;break-word&quot; normal=&quot;normal&quot; px=&quot;px&quot; sans-serif=&quot;sans-serif&quot; arial=&quot;arial&quot; yahei=&quot;yahei&quot; microsoft=&quot;microsoft&quot; ui=&quot;ui&quot; gb=&quot;gb&quot; sans=&quot;sans&quot; hiragino=&quot;hiragino&quot; sc=&quot;sc&quot; pingfang=&quot;pingfang&quot; neue=&quot;neue&quot; helvetica=&quot;helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;就我自己的经验来说，阅读也是分层次的，比如在网上看新闻、读公众号，这种属于碎片化阅读，它起到的是获取信息，或者就某一个点答疑解惑的作用。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p rgb=&quot;rgb&quot; important=&quot;important&quot; border-box=&quot;border-box&quot; em=&quot;em&quot; break-word=&quot;break-word&quot; normal=&quot;normal&quot; px=&quot;px&quot; sans-serif=&quot;sans-serif&quot; arial=&quot;arial&quot; yahei=&quot;yahei&quot; microsoft=&quot;microsoft&quot; ui=&quot;ui&quot; gb=&quot;gb&quot; sans=&quot;sans&quot; hiragino=&quot;hiragino&quot; sc=&quot;sc&quot; pingfang=&quot;pingfang&quot; neue=&quot;neue&quot; helvetica=&quot;helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;碎片化阅读貌似让我们得到更多信息，但阅读这些信息很少需要主动思考，甚至是一个完全被动接受的过程，仿佛使人上瘾一般，一条一条地不停读下去。长此以往，人们就会习惯性地被动接受碎片化的短信息，一些稍长的文段就会没耐心去读，更不用说主动思考事物发展背后的原因，变得懒惰，变得肤浅。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p rgb=&quot;rgb&quot; important=&quot;important&quot; border-box=&quot;border-box&quot; em=&quot;em&quot; break-word=&quot;break-word&quot; normal=&quot;normal&quot; px=&quot;px&quot; sans-serif=&quot;sans-serif&quot; arial=&quot;arial&quot; yahei=&quot;yahei&quot; microsoft=&quot;microsoft&quot; ui=&quot;ui&quot; gb=&quot;gb&quot; sans=&quot;sans&quot; hiragino=&quot;hiragino&quot; sc=&quot;sc&quot; pingfang=&quot;pingfang&quot; neue=&quot;neue&quot; helvetica=&quot;helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p rgb=&quot;rgb&quot; important=&quot;important&quot; border-box=&quot;border-box&quot; em=&quot;em&quot; break-word=&quot;break-word&quot; normal=&quot;normal&quot; px=&quot;px&quot; sans-serif=&quot;sans-serif&quot; arial=&quot;arial&quot; yahei=&quot;yahei&quot; microsoft=&quot;microsoft&quot; ui=&quot;ui&quot; gb=&quot;gb&quot; sans=&quot;sans&quot; hiragino=&quot;hiragino&quot; sc=&quot;sc&quot; pingfang=&quot;pingfang&quot; neue=&quot;neue&quot; helvetica=&quot;helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;如果说一本好书是一位作者最透彻的表达，那一本优秀的杂志就代表一种价值观的坚持，并不比一本书的分量轻。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p rgb=&quot;rgb&quot; important=&quot;important&quot; border-box=&quot;border-box&quot; em=&quot;em&quot; break-word=&quot;break-word&quot; normal=&quot;normal&quot; px=&quot;px&quot; sans-serif=&quot;sans-serif&quot; arial=&quot;arial&quot; yahei=&quot;yahei&quot; microsoft=&quot;microsoft&quot; ui=&quot;ui&quot; gb=&quot;gb&quot; sans=&quot;sans&quot; hiragino=&quot;hiragino&quot; sc=&quot;sc&quot; pingfang=&quot;pingfang&quot; neue=&quot;neue&quot; helvetica=&quot;helvetica&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;杂志，是快速扫描资讯和观念、获取灵感的方式。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;一本好的杂志，就像请了一个团队，帮你就某个主题出一份月度报告。哪怕只有一个图片有价值，也值回一二十块钱了。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
